title: How Fed tightening cycles end.jpg
description:
How Fed tightening cycles end

• The Fed typically hikes until something breaks
• By end-18 the Fed will be 9 hikes into a tightening cycle
• EM, credit, tech are all candidates in the cycle

BofA's conclusion: "Central bank liquidity = #1 driver of asset prices past decade."

And the liquidity is almost over.
